  Kau3 18 hoe3 e5 si5 kam2-sia7 Chu2 hou7 goa2 tit-tioh8 chit8 e5 ki-hoe7 thang choe3 khou2-hak8-seng, poaN3 choe3-kang poaN3 thak8-chheh e5 lou7 chiu7 khi3 jip8 Giu5-chin toa7-oh8. Khi2-thau5 chit8-ni5-ku2 chin peng5-siong5 chiam7-chiam7 keng-koe3, sou2 u7 e5 si5-kan long2 iong7 ti7 hak8-kho3, khiok bat thak8 goa7-chheh. Ti7 sou2 thak8 e5 goa7-chheh tiong Lo5--si7 sou2 tu3 e5 “Giam5-siok e5 hou-tiau3” (Law’s Serious Call to the Unconverted) hit-pun2 si7 goa2 siang7 jiat8-sim ai3 thak8 e5 chheh. Hit-si5 ti7 Giu5-chin tai7-hak8 u7 kui2-ui7 tong5-oh8, keng-siong5 ti7 pi2-chhu2 e5 khun2-pang5 lai7 chu7-hoe7, ki5-to2 gian2-kiu3 tho2-lun7. Chiah-e5 tai7-chi3 i2-keng sit8-heng5 liau2 kui2-na7-ni5. Oe7-su-li2 in hiaN-ti7 Iok-han7 kap Cha-li2 (John and Charles Wesley) si7 chit e5 se3-se3 e5 thoan5-the2 e5 leng2-siu3. In siu7 tong5-oh8 e5 leng2-chhio3 ki-chhi3, ka7 in ho7 che7-che7 mia5. U7-si5 kio3 in choe3 “Seng3-kiat-thoan5” (Holy Club), “Keng3-khian5-thoan5” (Godly Club), a2-si7 “Seng3-keng chiu3-thang5” (Bible Moths), kap “Sun5-kui-chia2” (Methodists). Tng goa2 jip8-oh8 e5 si5, chit e5 chip8-hoe7 chi2-u7 chhun 5, 6 e5 lang5 na7-tiaN7. Lang5 keng-the2 in choe3 “Sun5-kui-chia2”, si7 in-ui7 in e5 seng-oah8 thai3 kui-lut8-hoa3. Mui2-goeh8 peh-piaN2 siu2 boan2-chhan, siong5-siong5 khi3 tham3-mng7 peN7-lang5, a2-si7 kaN-hoan7. 
  Goa2 chin hi-bong7 ai3 ka-jip8 chit e5 chu7-hoe7, na7-si7 m7 kap in saN-bat, ji5-chhiaN2 chit8-si5 iu7 bo5 lang5 thang kai3-siau7 chiu7 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang ka-jip8. Keh chit8-ni5 au7 u7 chit8 e5 tek8-piat8 e5 ki-hoe7, goa2 chiu7 kap Cha-li2 Oe7-su-li2 (Charles Wesley) sek8-sai7. U7 chit8-jit8 u7 chit8 e5 san3-hiong hu7-jin5-lang5 iam3-se3 khi3 chu7-sat, heng7-tit chu7-sat bo5 si2, goa2 chiu7 sia2 chit8-tiuN phoe chhiaN2 ti7 goan2 hau7-lai7 teh be7 pin-ko2 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 theh8 hou7 Oe7-su-li2 sian-siN, chhiaN2 in khi3 tham3-hong2 hit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5. Ia7 kio3 hit e5 lau7 a-po5 m7-thang kong2 goa2 e5 mia5, bo5 phah-sng3 hit e5 a-po5 soa3 chiong goa2 e5 mia5 ka7 in kong2. Cha-li2 koe3-khi3 bat thiaN-kiN3 goa2 ia7 bat khi3 tham3 kaN-gak8 e5 hoan7-lang5, ia7 chham-ka kau3-khu e5 seng3-chhan, koh si5-siong5 bat gu7-kiN3 goa2 ka-ki7 chit8 e5 teh san3-pou7, tui3 an2-ni i hoaN-hi2 chiap-siu7 goa2 e5 phoe, soa3 kio3 hit e5 lau7 a-po5 lai5 chio goa2 saN-kap ti7 bin5-a2-jit8 choe3-hoe2 chiah8 tiong-tau3-tng3. Goa2 e5 sim tu2-tu2 him-bou7 ai3 tit-tioh8 u7 siok8-leng5 e5 peng5-iu2. I ia7 chin khoai3 chiu7 chai goa2 si7 chit e5 i3-su3, chiu7 sang3 goa2 chit8-pun2 Hoat-lan5-khek sou2 tu3 e5 “Lun7 m7 kiaN lang5” (Franke’s Treatise Against the Fear of Man) kap “Kau3-bok8 e5 tiong-ko3” (The County Parson’s Advice to His Parishioners) chit nng7-pun2 chheh. Keh liau2 bo5 loa7-ku2, chiu7 koh hou7 goa2 chit8-pun2 “Sin5 e5 oah8-mia7 ti7 lang5 e5 lai7-bin7” (The Life of God in the Soul of Man). Goa2 chiong5-lai5 m7-chai sim2-mih8 si7 chin-sit8 e5 keng3-khian5, tit8 kau3 Siong7-te3 chiong chit-pun2 ho2 e5 chheh sang3 kau3 goa2 chhiu2-nih8 goa2 chiah chai. Sin5 liam-piN chi2-si7 goa2, chin-sit8 e5 keng3-khian5 chiu7-si7 lang5 kap Sin5 e5 lian5-hap8, si7 Ki-tok e5 khoan2-sit chiaN5-choe3 ti7 lan2 e5 lai7-bin7. Chit-si5 goa2 chiah hiau2-ngou7 lang5 tek-khak tioh8 chiaN5-choe3 chit8-e5 chhong3-cho7 e5 lang5. Chhin-chhiuN7 hit e5 Sat-ma2-li7-a e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chit8-iuN7. Goa2 sia2 p