  Tui3 an2-ni goa2 chiu7 khai-si2 u7 kui-lut8 e5 seng-oah8, m7-ai3 phah-sng2 chit8-sut-a2 si5-kan. Put-lun7 in khi3 tham3 piN7-lang5, a2-si7 pang-chan7 song3-hiong-lang5, chham-ka in it-chhe3 e5 oah8-tang7, sim-lai7 kam2-kak chin song2-khoai3. Chong2-si7 ho2 kong-keng2 bo5 thang ku2, bian2 loa7 ku2, phoa3-piN7-kui2 put-si5 lai5 kau-tiN5, ti3-kau3 goa2 tioh8 chiam7-si5 theng5-chi2 it-chhe3 e5 oah8-tang7. Na7-si7 goa2 tui3 it-chhe3 e5 kiu3-un khiok it-hoat chheng-chho2, ia7 leng2-to7 chit8-ui7 tong5-oh8 kui Chu2. 
