  U7 goa7 choe7 tong5-oh8 tu2-tioh8 chhi3-lian7 kau3 chhiu2 e5 si5 long2 li7-khui goan2 khi3. Tui3 tok-hak8 e5 hoan2-tui3 ia7 choe7-choe7 tong5-oh8 kiu khi3. “Ai3-bou7 lang5 e5 o-lo2, khah koe3-thau5 ti7 ai3-bou7 tui3 Sin5 lai5 e5 o-lo2, kap chit8-chiong2 pi-phi2 khut-hok8-seng3 kiaN lang5 biau2-si7 khoaN3-khin e5 sim, ti3-kau3 hou7 che7-che7 lang5 hoan2-poe7 khi3-sak goan2.” Goa2 (Hoai5-tek-hui) si7 chit8 e5 song3-hiong e5 khou2-hak8 seng, tui3 ka-jip8 sun5-kui-thoan5 kap Oe7-su-li2 in ong2-lai5 i2-au7, koh khah si7 siu7 lang5 chiong2-chiong2 e5 bu2-jiok8. Goa2 siong5-siong5 siu7 lang5 tim3 la5-sam5-mih8, u7 e5 pak-siah goa2 e5 kang-chiN5, u7 nng7-ui7 goa2 ti-ki2 e5 peng5-iu2, khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 koat-sim hu7-khi2 sip8-ji7-ke3 beh kun-toe3 Ki-tok, chiu7 liah8 goa2 choe3 thang kian3-siau3--e5, kau3-boe2 keng2-jian5 pang3-sak goa2. Lian5 iN7-tiuN2 ia7 siong5-siong5 hang2-hoah goa2. Sim7-chi3 u7 chit8-pai2 haN2 kong2 beh ka7 goa2 kek-chhut oh8. Kong2 goa2 na7 koh ke3-siok8 khi3 tham3 peN7-lang5, song3-hiong e5 lang5 tek-khak m7 pang3 goa2 soah. Goa2 khi2-thau5 thiaN liau2 chin kiaN, chiu7 khut-hok8 chit e5 ui-hek, na7-si7 bian2 koh loa7-ku2 goa2 chiu7 koh ho2-taN2 khi2--lai5, chiu7 chiau3-siong5 koh ui7 Chu2 kang-chok. Kai-chai3 u7 chit8-ui7 chin jin5-chu5 e5 to7-su (chi2-to7 e5 sian-siN) siong5-siong5 eng7 chheh chioh--goa2, tui3 goa2 kek8 ho2 cheng5-i3, chiong5-lai5 m7-bat hoan2-tui3 goa2 e5 kang-chok, put-ko3 i si7 kong2 goa2 tui3 sin3-giong2 u7 khah koe3-thau5 jiat8-sim. 
  Goa2 ti7 Kat-lo5-su-tek e5 chhin-iu2, tui3 goa2 sia2-phoe hou7 in chai goa2 u7 kai2-pian3 liau2-au7, in chin gong5-ngiah8 kiaN-hiaN5, tui3 goa2 seN-chhut kiong5-liat8 e5 phian-kian3, sim7-chi3 u7 lang5 kong2 goa2 si7 khi2 siau2. Na7-si7 goa2 liah8 chiah-e5 choe3 se3-se3 e5 chhi3-lian7 hoan2-tng2 si7 u7 li7-ek goa2. Bian2 loa7-ku2 goa2 chiu7 hoat-hian7 tioh8 lang5 ui7-tioh8 Chu2 e5 mia5 lai5 li7-khui pe7-bo2, bou2-kiaN2, a2-si7 chhan5-hng5 chhu3-theh8--e5, bo5 m7-beh tit-tioh8 pah-poe7 e5 po3-siuN2. 
