  Tng-si5 goa2 e5 sim-keng2, tui3 goa2 thau5-pai2 chhiN2-ngou7 i2-au7, goa2 kam2-kak u7 chit8-chiong2 tek8-piat8 e5 iau chhui3-ta, him-bou7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 khiam-sun3, koh ho2 chhin-chhiuN7 Ki-tian5 tui3 Sou3-kat e5 lang5 kong2 “Goa2 chiu7 beh eng7 khong3-ia2 e5 chhi3 kap chhi3-a2 phah-siong lin2 e5 bah.” Sin5 chiau3-iuN7 ia7 iong7 kok-chiong2 kiong5-liat8 e5 chhi3-giam7 lai5 ka3-si7 in2-chhoa7 goa2. Pun2-lai5 goa2 chhin-kun7 Sin5 e5 si5 siong5-siong5 si7 kam2-kak chin tiN-bit8 chin bi2-ho2. Chiah-e5 an-ui3 bian2 loa7-ku2 Sin5 long2 siu khi2--lai5, hoan2-tng2 eng7 thang kiaN--e5 lai5 ap-to2 goa2. Goa2 chheng2-kau3 goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 Cha-li2 Oe7-su-li2, i khou2-khng3 goa2 tioh8 keng2-seng2 kin2-siu2, hou7 goa2 chit8-pun2 chham-kho2-su chiu7-si7 Kheng2-poe5 To-ma2 e5 “Hau7-hoat Ki-tok” (The Imitation of Christ by Thomas a3 Kempis). Chit-chiong2 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 tang7-taN3 tiok8-chiam7 cheng-ka, hou7 goa2 sit khi3 sou2 u7 bek8-siong2 e5 leng5-lek8, sim7-chi3 su-siuN2 e5 leng5-lek8 tou kam2-kak ti5-tun7 khi3. Chi2-u7 Sin5 Siong7-te3 chai-iaN2, u7 che7-che7 pai2 goa2 tng5-tng5 mi5 to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5-teng2, ui7-tioh8 sou2 kam2-kak e5 tang7-taN3, haiN-haiN-chhan bo5 soah. Kui-jit8, kui le2-pai3, goa2 phak-loh8 ti7 te7-bin7, kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 goa2 chu7-iu5, chin2-kiu3 goa2 thoat-li7 tui3 te7-gek8-nih8 chhut--lai5 hit-khoan2 kiau-ngou7 e5 su-siuN2, hiah e5 su-siuN2 siong5-siong5 kheh-jip8-lai5 goa2 e5 thau5-nau2-nih8, lai5 hun-loan7 goa2 e5 sim-su7. Hou7 goa2 seN-khi2 chu7-ai3, chiau3 ka-ki7 e5 i3-su3, kiau-ngou7, chit-tou3, tit8-tit8 lun5-liu5 lai5 kiau2-jiau2 goa2, chong2-si7 goa2 koat-sim beh iaN5 koe3 chiah-e5. Che-iuN7 keng-koe3 liau2 kui2-na7 goeh8-jit8, goa2 iu5-goan5 hoat-hian7 kiau-ngou7 ia7-si7 chiau3-ku7 chham-jip8 ti7 goa2 e5 su-siuN2, chha-put-to it-chhe3 e5 gian5-gu2 tong7-chok i to long2-chong2 u7 ti7 hit che7-che7 lai7-bin7. Ti7 chit-khoan2 sim bo5 chheng bo5 hoaN-hi2 e5 e7-bin7, u7 chit8-jit8 thak8-tioh8 Koa--si7 tu3 e5 “Siok8-leng5 e5 chian3-cheng” (Custa