  Goa2 chha-put-to u7 6 le2-pai3 e5 ku2, ka-ki7 koaiN ti7 thak8-chheh-pang5-lai7. Hian7-chai7 koh tit-tioh8 am3-si7, beh sit8-heng5 koh-khah giam5-keh e5 che3-iok8. Goa2 mui2 le2-pai3 kim3-chiah8 nng7-pai2, goa2 e5 chheng7-chhah si7 chin phok-sou3. Goa2 siuN7 chit8 e5 chham3-hoe2 e5 lang5 thau5-mng5 m7 eng3-kai boah-iu5. Goa2 koa3 iuN5-mng5 e5 chhiu2-tho3, chheng7 u7 pou2 e5 saN, chheng7 am-cham e5 phoe5-e5. Chu7-cha2 goa2 chiu7 chai chap8-hun beng5-pek8 Siong7-te3 e5 kok, put-chai7 lim-chiah8 na7-si7 goa2 kian-koat beh sit8-heng5 chiah-e5 su7, chu7-goan7 pang3-sak ka-ki7, in-ui7 goa2 siuN7 choe3 chiah-e5 e7 pang-chan7 goa2 chin3-pou7 ti7 siok8-leng5 e5 oah8-mia7. Kau3 chit-si5 goa2 i2-keng pang3-sak goa2 e5 it-chhe3, koh bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 thang pang3-sak lah. Tu5 hui hong3-khi3 kong7-tong5 e5 chu7-hoe7, kap li7-khui khi3-sak keng3-khian5 e5 peng5-iu2. Goa2 i2-keng bo5 ki3 jit8-ki3 lah, bo5 chhut-siaN ki5-to2 lah, ia7 m7 tham3 peN7-lang5 kap siu5-hoan7 lah. Hian7-chai7 koh lai5 chit8 e5 am3-si7, ai3 goa2 ui7-tioh8 Ki-tok e5 ian5-kou3 li7-khui goa2 e5 keng3-khian5 e5 peng5-iu2. Ho2, goa2 ia7 koat-i3 beh hoan2-poe7 khi3-sak in. Keh-jit8 goa2 m7-khi3 chham-ka cheng3 hiaN-ti7 pai3-saN e5 kim3-chiah8, hoan2-tng2 chhut-khi3 kau3 ia2-goa7, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 bek8-to2. Goa2 ia7 m7 hu3 am3-si5 e5 chu7-hoe7. Keh cha2-khi2 koh m7 chiau3 iok kap Cha-li2 Oe7-su-li2 saN-kap chiah8 cha2-khi2-tng3. Tui3 chiah-e5 su7 hou7 Oe7-su-li2 hoat-seng giau5-gi5 lah. I lai5 kau3 goa2 e5 pang5-keng, chin khoai3 hoat-hian7 goa2 e5 khoan2-sit, kin2 chiong goa2 e5 gui5-hiam2 ka7 goa2 kong2, ji5-chhiaN2 kai3-siau7 goa2 kap Oe7-su-li2 Iok-han7 (John Wesley) saN bat, in-ui7 i ti7 siok8-leng5 e5 oah8-mia7-chiuN7 pi2-kau3 khah u7 keng-giam7. Goa2 kap Iok-han7 kong2-oe7, i khou2-khng3 goa2 khoe-hok8 goa2 chiong5-chian5 it-chhe3 e5 oah8-tang7, chong2-si7 choat8-tui3 m7-thang oa2-kho3 chiah-e5 heng5-ui5. Choe3-au7 tui3 ti7 i ho2 e5 tiong-khok, chiu7 tit-tioh8 tui3 sat-tan3 e5 khui2-ke3 tiong siu7 chin2-kiu3 