  Sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni goa2 choat8-tui3 be7-e7 to5-pi7 chiah-e5 ka-ki7 ke-thiN e5 heng5-hoat8. Tui3 ti7 goa2 ka-ki7 ku2-ku2 khou2-chhou2 ka-ki7, ti3-kau3 hou7 goa2 e5 the2-lat8 toa7-toa7 soe-jiok8. Sim7-chi3 kau3-boe2 soa3 bo5 lat8 thang peh lau5-thui. Goa2 hit-si5 put-tek-i2 tioh8 thong-ti hit-ui7 jin5-chu5 e5 to7-su, tui3 i chhut-chiN5 pheng3-chhiaN2 i-seng lai5 khoaN3--goa2. Tong5-oh8 tit-tioh8 thang kong-kek e5 peN3, chiu7 chin tek-i3 toa7-siaN han2-hoa7, kong2, “KhoaN3 ah! I e5 kim3-chiah8 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8 kiat-ko2.” Chong2-si7 goa2 sim-lai7 ka-ki7 chu7-ui3, seng-khu sui-jian5 siau-san2, na7-si7 goa2 e5 leng5-mia7 khiok hoan2-tng2 ka-kiong5. Goa2 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni piN7 to2 ti7 chhng5-nih8 40 goa7 jit8-ku2, goa2 kam2-kak si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 hou7 goa2 eng5-kng e5 kian3-chek, keng-koe3 ku2-ku2 e5 leng2-cheng7 sit-i3, na7-si7 kau3-boe2 tit-tioh8 Chu2 eng5-kng e5 thau2-pang3. Pi-ai e5 lang5 i2-keng koe3-khi3, ju5-kim chiu7 toa7-toa7 beng5-pek8 tiam3-ti7 Chu2 lai7-bin7 e5 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8. Keng-koe3 siu7 khi3-sak kap chhi3-lian7 ou-am3 e5 mi5 liau2-au7, chiu7 koh hng7-hng7 khoaN3 tioh8 hit-liap8 ia7 na7-chun2 u7 khoaN3-tioh8, ia7 na2-chun2 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8, u7-si5 hou7 hun5 kham3--leh, u7-si5 chhut-hian7 chhut--lai5 e5 kng-chhiN, ah! Tiong5-sin chhut-hian7 lah! Na2-chun2 thiN-kng-cha2 ng3-bang7 e5 khe2-beng5-chhiN, koh chit8-pai2 chhan3-lan7 kng-chio3 ti7 goa2 sim-tiong lah! 
