  Chu2-au7 1737 ni5 goa2 siong5-siong5 chiap-tioh8 Oe7-su-li2 in hiaN-ti7 tui3 Bi2-kok kia3 lai5 hou7 goa2 e5 phoe. Ka7 goa2 kong2 Kiau-ti-a chiu (Georgia) e5 kang-chok. Tui3 hit-si5 khi2 goa2 chiu7 seN-khi2 jiat8-jiat8 ai3 chhut-kok e5 sim, ng3-bang7 thang ti7 hia pang-chan7 in choe3 kang. Goa2 chiu7 sia7-choat8 it-chhe3 e5 chiau-chheng2 koat-i3 beh khi3 Bi2-chiu. Kau3 Cha-li2 to3-lai5 Lun5-tun liau2-au7, keng3 koh-khah chhui-chhok goa2 li7-khui Eng-kok khi3 Bi2-kok. Iok-han7 ia7 sia2-phoe lai5 chhiaN2 goa2 khi3 tang5 kang. Ti7 kia3--lai5 e5 phoe tiong bio5-sia2 in e5 kang-chok chong7-hong2, jian5-au7 kong2: “Chi2-u7 Tat8-la-mou5-the5 (Mr. Delamotte) kap goa2 ti7 chia, tit8-tit8 theng3-hau7 kau3 Siong7-te3 kam2-tong7 I e5 lou5-pok8 e5 sim, kau3 hou7 hiah e5 lang5 kam-goan7 chiong in e5 siN3-mia7 kau-tai3 ti7 I e5 chhiu2, chin3-cheng5 lai5 pang-chan7 goan2. Hoai5-tek-hui kun, li2 na7-si7 Sin5 sou2 beh kam2-tong7 sou2 ai3 chhe-khian2 e5 lang5, li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 tah-eng3 Siong7-te3 nih8? Li2 na7 mng7 goa2, u7 sim2-mih8 siu-jip8 a2-bo5? U7 mih8 thang chiah8, u7 saN thang chheng7, u7 chhu3 thang toa3, che-si7 li2 e5 Chu2 sou2 bo5--e5, na7-si7 u7 eng2-oan2 be7 soe-the3 be7 pai7-hoai7 eng5-kng e5 bian2-liu5.” Goa2 thak8 liau2 chiah-e5 oe7, goa2 e5 sim-lai7 chhin-chhiuN7 teh tio5-thiau3 e5 hoaN-hi2. Ki5-u5 iau2 u7 che7-che7 khoan5-keng2, tu2-tu2 phoe3-hap8 hou7 goa2 it-hoat chheng-chho2 beng5-pek8 goa2 sou2 tioh8 kiaN5 e5 lou7. Thau5 chit8 hang7 Oe7-su-li2 si7 goa2 chi3-ho2 e5 peng5-iu2. Bi2-kok Kiau-ti-a chiu si7 chit8 e5 chin iu3-ti7 e5 sit8-bin5-te7. Cheng3-hu2 chin koan-sim hit e5 te7-hng e5 hok-li7, ji5-chhiaN2 hu7-kin7 thiaN kong2 u7 chin che7 In3-te7-an (Ang5-sek e5 hoan-a2) lang5. Che7-chun5 koe3 iuN5 e5 su7 chiau3 goa2 (Hoai5-tek-hui) e5 seng-khu tai7-khai3 bo5 iau3-kin2. Keng-koe3 chap8-ji7-hun e5 chhim-siuN7 ki5-to2 e5 kiat-ko2, goa2 chiu7 koat-sim chhut-hoat khi3 Bi2-kok Kiau-ti-a chiu. Goa2 chhim-chai na7 kap goa2 e5 chhin-chhek chham-siong5 un2-tang3 e