  Bo5 phah-sng3 kau3 Lun5-tun, chiah chai li7 chhut-hoat e5 ki5-kan iau2 chin ku2, chiu7 li7-iong7 chit e5 si5-kan ti7 tak8 sou2-chai7 choe3 kang. Goa2 ti7 tak8 sou2-chai7 kong2 “Ti7 Ki-tok Ia5-sou nih8 teng5-thau5-siN e5 seng3-chit kap su-iau3,” tui3 chit phiN to7-li2 u7 tiam2-toh8 Kat-lo5-su-tek, Put-liat8-su-tok, Kap Lun5-tun chiah-e5 kau3-hoe7 hok8-heng e5 hoe2. Goa2 khai-si2 chhai2-chhu2 chit8-chiong2 kang-chok heng5-sek, au7-lai5 chiong-sin chiau3 an2-ni khi3 kiaN5, thau5-boe2 m7-bat pin5-toaN7. Chit-chiong2 heng5-sek su-iau3 siau-mou5 chin-che7 the2-lek8 kap nau2-lek8, u7-si5 ti3-kau3 goa2 e5 seng-khu teh beh tong3 be7 tiau5. Peng5-iu2 siong5-siong5 khou2-khng3 goa2 tioh8 po2-sioh ka-ki7, chong2-si7 goa2 siong5-siong5 in3 kong2 “Goa2 leng7-khou2 kam-goan7 eng7-chin7, m7-goan7 he7 teh chhau3-noa7. Ti7 Siong7-te3 sou2 su3 e5 si5-kan lai7, koat-toan3 m7-chun2 eng5-eng5 lai5 hoaN-hi2, khoaN3-oah8, hi3-hiauh, thit-tho5.” 
