  Goa2 ti7 Bi2-kok chiah u7 4 goeh8-jit8, chiu7 koh to3-tng2 lai5 Eng-kok, chit8-bin7 ui7-tioh8 pan7-li2 chit8-koa2 pit-iau3 e5 chhiu2-siok8, leng7-goa7 chit8-bin7 u7 hu7-tam ai3 ti7 Kiat-ti-a khai-pan7 kou-ji5-iN7, ng3-bang7 to3-lai5 e7-thang tit8-tioh8 pang-chan7. Kau3 to3-lai5 Eng-kok liau2-au7, chiah hoat-hian7 cheng5-se3 toa7 pian3-oaN7, u7 che7-che7 thoan5-kau3-ka khoaN3 goa2 choe3 tui3-tek8, chi2-u7 kek8 sio2-sou3 e5 kang2-toaN5 chun2-goa2 kong2. Choe3 te7-it hou7 kau3-kai3 it-poaN e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2 bo5 hoaN-hi2 e5, chiu7-si7 kong2 goa2 ui5-hoan2 chai7-lai5 e5 kau3-kui, chiau3 peng5-iu2 e5 iau-kiu5, ti7 in e5 ka-teng5 lai5 kang2-ian2 khui-thiah seng3-keng. Chit hang7-su7 chiu7 u7 lek8-su2 i2-lai5 boe7 bat u7 an2-ni, koat-toan3 be7-tit iong5-un2. In-ui7 an2-ni goa2 ti7 Lun5-tun chiong-kun7 chit8 goeh8-jit8, be7 tit chiuN7-tai5 lai5 kang2 to7. Siang7-khoan2 ia7 hoat-seng ti7 Pit-liat8-su-tok, ti7 hia nng7 le2-pai3 ku2 iau2-ku2 bo5 ki-hoe7. Chi2-u7 Niu2-kai3 (Newgate) kaN-gak8 e5 khan3-siu2 chun2 goa2 tui3 kaN-hoan7 lai5 thoan5-to7, chong2-si7 chhi7-tiuN2 iu7 chhut-lai5 kan-siap8, ti3-kau3 kaN-gak8 e5 mng5-lou7 ia7 koaiN khi3. 
  Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 khou2-khng3 goa2 bo5 pit-iau3 koh to3-tng2 khi3 Bi2-kok choe3 kang, tui3 goa2 kong2: “Ho5-pit tioh8 chhut kok nih8? Chit sou2-chai7 kiam2-bo5 In3-te7-an lang5? Ka2-su2 li2 iu2-i3 ai3 in2-chhoa7 In3-te7-an lang5 hoan2-hoe2, Kheng3-su-ou (Kingswood) hu7-kun7 Put-liat8-su-tok, u7 kau3-giah8 che7 e5 khong3-hu kho2-i2 chin2-kiu3 ah!” Goa2 siuN7 kong2 u7-iaN2, kang2-tai5 m7-kheng2 hou7 goa2 kang2-to7, na7-si7 kho2-lian5 e5 khong3-hu in-ui7 khiam3-khoeh chai-bat chiu7 tim5-lun5, goa2 chiu7 khi3 hia, khia7 ti7 se3-se3 e5 soaN-lun5-a2 teng2 ng3 200 goa7 e5 khong3-hu lai5 kong2 to7-li2. Kam2-sia7 o-lo2 Siong7-te3, thoe3 goa2 tu5-khi3 it-chhe3 e5 chou2-tong3 ka7 goa2 khui-lou7, goa2 chiu7 koat-sim kau3 ia2-goa7 khi3 choe3 kang. Goa2 siuN7 chit-khoan2 kang-chok, hek8-chia2 chiu7-si7 oh8 chhong3-cho7 e5 chu2-chaiN2 e5 hong-hoat. I chiong toa7-soaN choe3 i e5 kang2-tai5, ng3 khong-tiong lai5 kong2-pou3 i e5 siaN-im, Iu5-thai3 lang5 ku7-choat8 I e5 hok-im, I chiu7 chhe-khian2 I e5 lou5-pok8 chhut-khi3 kau3 toa7-lou7 teng2 li5-pa-piN lai5 chio-hou lang5. 
  Chit e5 siau-sit lip8-khek thoan5-khui. Te7 ji7 pai2 chiu7 u7 chit8-ban7 lang5 i2-siong7 lai5 chu7-chip8 thiaN goa2 kang2-to7, chhiu7-a2-kha li5-pa-piN long2 kheh-moa2 kho2-lian5 e5 lang5. Ti7 chiah-e5 kang-chok e5 jit8-chi2 long2-si7 hiah e5 bin7 ou-ou kap chheng7 la5-sam5 lam5-lui2 e5 i-chiuN5 e5 lang5 lai5 thiaN. Goa2 kong2 kui tiam2-cheng, theng3-chiong3 long2 an-cheng7 bo5 kiau2-jiau2 e5 siaN-im, siaN-im e5 toa7, kau3-giah8 hou7 choan5-the2 long2 e7-tit thiaN-tioh8. In ki3-jian5 bo5 u7 ka-ki7 e5 gi7, a2-si7 sim2-mih8 thang siuN7 choe3 ho2--e5 thang pang3-sak, chai sim-lai7 sou2 u7 chhiong-moa2--e5 long2 si7 phaiN2, chiu7 hoaN-hi2 thiaN kong2 u7 chit8-ui7 Ia5-sou, I si7 thiu-hiong3--e5 kap choe7-jin5 e5 peng5-iu2, I lai5 m7-si7 beh chio gi7 lang5, si7 beh chio choe7-jin5 hoe2-kai2. Theng3-chiong3 ko2-jian5 toa7 siu7 kam2-tong7, che7-che7 lang5 lau5 bak8-sai2, hau2-kau3 phiN7-lau5 noa7-tih. Che7-che7 lang5 chin-chiaN3 hoan2-hoe2 chiap-lap8 Chu2 Ia5-sou, au7-lai5 tui3 in e5 sou2-kiaN5 lai5 cheng3-beng5 in ko2-jian5 u7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. 
  Put-liat8-su-tok e5 le2-pai3-tng5 oan5-choan5 ng3 goa2 hong-so2, chong2-si7 peh-siN3 khiok chhin-chhiuN7 iau chhui3-ta e5 him-bou7 Siong7-te3 oah8-mia7 e5 oe7. An2-ni beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3-nih8? Goa2 chit8-sut-a2 to bo5 tiu-tu5, chi2-koan2 na7 u7 ki-hoe7 chiu7 hong7 Chu2 e5 mia5 lai5 chin3-cheng5. M7-bian2 goa7-ku2 goa2 chiu7 ti7 that-kiu5 e5 chhau2-pou (Bowling Green) khui-khoah e5 sou2-chai7 lai5 pou3-to7. Siong7-te3 ai3 beh choe3-kang, chi7-chui7 e7-thang chou2-tong3 nih8? KaN-gak8 ng3 goa2 koaiN-mng5, A-che2 e5 chhu3 bo5 kau3 thang iong5-un2 le2-pai3-jit8 lai5 chip8-hoe7 si3-hun7-chit8 e5 lang5, an2-ni Siong7-te3 chiu7 hou7 goan2 siuN7-tioh8, lang5 chiu7 chiong chit8-ui7 toa7 that-kiu5-tiuN5 hou7 goan2 eng7, hou7 goa2 ti7 hia thang ng3 chiong-kin7 5000 lang5 lai5 kang2-to7. 
  Goa2 sui-jian5 siu7 tioh8 toa7-kun5 e5 tui3-tek8 si3-bin7 kong-kek, khiok bo5 ti3-kau3 kam2-kak khun3-khou2, hoan2-tng2 kam2-kak u7 kong2 boe7-chhut e5 song2-khoai3, in-ui7 chai ti7 thN-nih8 e5 Chu2-lang5 u7 hoaN-hi2 goa2 e5 hok8-sai7. U7 che7-che7 lang5 lai5 chhoe7 goa2, lai5 chhoe7-kiu5 siok8-leng5 e5 an-ui3 kap chi2-to7. Goa2 siong5-siong5 ti7 jit8-si5 kang2-to7 kui2-na7-pai2, am3-si5 ke3-siok8 tap-hok8 sou2 mng7 e5 bun7-te5, kai2-koat long2-chong2 e5 giau5-gi5 kap khun3-lan5. Na7-si7 goa2 u7 chhiong-moa2 chin-toa7 e5 hoaN-hi2 kap khoai3-lok8. Goa2 siong5-siong5 kam2-kak chit8 le2-pai3 chin khoai3-koe3. Goa2 sit8-chai7 kho2-lian5 ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 thou2-khui3 si5-kan oh koe3 e5 lang5. Chi2-iau3 in thiaN3 Ki-tok, eng7 choan5-pou7 e5 si5-kan lai5 hong7-hian3 hou7 Chu2, in chiu7 be7 chhoe7-tioh8 iu-ut e5 si5-kan. U7 lang5 thiaN tioh8 goa2 kong2 siu7 khun2-tiok8 chiu7 kam2-kak chin ki5-koai3 kiaN-hiaN5, siuN7 kong2 se3-kai3 to i2-keng Ki-tok-hoa3 lah, thai2-tho2 iau2 u7 khun2-pek? Chong2-si7 chin kho2-sioh, ka2-su2 Ki-tok chit-si5 hoaN-hi2 lim5-kau3 te7-chiuN7, I ia7-si7 beh siu7 tioh8 chiong5-chian5 tang5-khoan2 e5 khou2-chhou2. Chi7-chui7 beh ui7-tioh8 I chhut-khi3 thoan5-iong5 hok-im, chiu7 eng3-kai ki5-thai7 cha2 su3-tou5 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 thai7-gu7. Chu2 ah! Kiu5 Li2 pi7-pan7 goa2, lai5 eng3-hu3 jim7-ho5 e5 su7-pian3. Kau3 ui7-tioh8 Li2 e5 ian5-kou3 lai5 siu7 lang5 liap8-cho7 phaiN2-oe7, goa2 su7-sit8 chiaN3 chiaN3 eng7 chit e5 choe3 khoai3-lok8, in-ui7 goa2 e5 Chu2-lang5 Li2 cha2-cha2 ia7 i2-keng tai7-seng goa2 siu7-lang5 e5 hui2-pong3. 
